com.microsoft.azure.sdk.iot.deps.serializer

Interface TwinChangedCallback

  • Deprecated. 
    As of release 0.4.0, this interface is not necessary anymore.

    @Deprecated
public interface TwinChangedCallback
    INNER TWINPARSER CLASS An interface for an IoT Hub Device Twin callback. Developers are expected to create an implementation of this interface, and the transport will call execute(Map) upon receiving a property or tags changes from an IoT Hub Device Twin.
